Title: omd start mkeventd: Error Code of Event Daemon
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: omd
Date: 1706877168
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0p40

The command <code>omd start mkeventd</code> starts the event daemon. Previously, any exit code produced
by this daemon would be ignored. Now, if the exit code is non-zero, then the message <code>Failed</code> is
shown and the command <code>omd start mkeventd</code> exits with error code 2.
